  "knownIntentionalDifferences": [
    "The new package adds DOM-free layout, adapter extraction, React rendering, edit handles, debug boxes, badge pointers, and package-prefixed pa-annotation classes.",
    "Package annotation overlays are pointer-transparent by default while edit handles opt back into pointer events for authoring.",
    "The Bronto CSS bridge is styling-only and must not depend on @ponchia/ui at runtime.",
    "When a local @ponchia/ui checkout is available, upstream parity checks compare legacy selector coverage, legacy CSS declaration properties, custom properties, keyframes, and helper exports."
